text: The 2019 season is the 90th season of the KLFA League, which is a Malaysian football competition featuring semi-professional and amateur clubs from Kuala Lumpur.Tentera Darat FA are the defending champions. ==Super League== ===League table=== ==Division 1== ===League table=== ==References== ==External links== * Official Kuala Lumpur FA 4 Malay
